welcome_message_body: Welcome to Keystone, where the charming small town atmosphere meets breathtaking natural beauty. Get ready to discover our historic sites, outdoor adventures, and friendly community. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories in Keystone!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily domestic airlines.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C is one of four satellite terminals at Tampa International Airport, serving primarily international airlines.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport, with a 2-hour time limit per session.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Executive Airport offers a variety of services and amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Jet Terminal
terminals.description: The private jet terminal at Executive Airport provides luxury and convenience for those flying on private aircraft.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's WiFi network for free.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport serves both commercial and military flights.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Mac Dill AFB Airport is used exclusively for military flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport serves all commercial flights and includes amenities such as a food court, gift shops, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport caters to private and chartered flights, offering a luxurious lounge and concierge services.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St. Petersburg-Clearwater International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whitted Airport provides services for both commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Whitted Airport offers exclusive services for private jet owners and their guests.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network throughout the terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Zephyrhills Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Zephyrhills Airport is exclusively for private and chartered flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport terminal.
